{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893350/extras/RoadMap3_Cropped.png?t=1737979410\" /><strong>JOIN OUR DISCORD   </strong>The game is still in early development so the demo is bound to change a lot.   <br>join the discord to have an impact on the game!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into a realm where divinity meets humanity in Liftlands, a medieval fantasy city-builder. As a fledgling god, you wield the power to shape lives and landscapes. Guide your devout followers from the dawn of civilization to the heights of a mystical empire. Balance the benevolent acts of creation with the might of divine wrath, all while defending against the encroaching darkness that threatens your worshipers. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Divine Interaction</strong>: <br>Directly manipulate the world with your cursor-hand of god. Lift villagers, shape terrains, and bestow miracles.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893350/extras/Divine_intervention.gif?t=1737979410\" /></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Villager Symbiosis</strong>: <br>Your power grows with your people's faith. Cultivate their society, and they will uphold your divine legacy.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893350/extras/Fulfilling_Prayers.gif?t=1737979410\" /></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ritualistic Progression</strong>: <br>Perform sacred rituals to unlock potent abilities. Each choice, a testament to your strategic divinity. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893350/extras/Rituals.gif?t=1737979410\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Medieval Fantasy Setting</strong>: <br>Explore enchanting forests, erect towering citadels, and discover ancient magic woven into the fabric of the world.  <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893350/extras/Setting.gif?t=1737979410\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Strategic Challenges</strong>: <br>Face the trials of the night with strategic prowess, as darkness brings forth creatures that test the strength of your divine mettle. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893350/extras/Challanges.gif?t=1737979410\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embrace your godhood and carve your path through history in Liftlands \u2014 where your will shapes the destiny of all.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2893350?t=1737979410","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893350/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1737979410","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893350/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737979410","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893350/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737979410","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2898460,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2893350/extras/RoadMap3_Cropped.png?t=1737979410\" /><strong>JOIN OUR DISCORD   </strong>The game is still in early development so the demo is bound to change a lot.   <br>join the discord to have an impact on the game!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into a realm where divinity meets humanity in Liftlands, a medieval fantasy city-